sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant B as Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    C->>B: POST /api/auth/login
    B->>B: Validate input
    B->>DB: Find user by email
    DB-->>B: User record

    alt User not found
        B-->>C: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    B->>B: Verify password

    alt Password mismatch
        B-->>C: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    B->>DB: Count active tokens
    DB-->>B: tokenCount

    alt tokenCount >= 3
        B->>DB: Revoke oldest token
    end

    B->>B: Sign JWT access token
    B->>B: Generate refresh token
    B->>DB: Store refresh token hash
    B-->>C: 200 {accessToken, refreshToken}
